data.description: Location, Location, Location!!! Nice, 3 bedroom, 2 bath brick home with CHA, metal roof & 2-car garage on 34 acres with Highway 177 frontage. Spacious kitchen with lots of cabinets and all appliances to stay. Large living room with wood burning fireplace. New laminate wood flooring in living room & bedrooms. Additional room w/stained concrete floor could be a 4th bedroom, den or office. Home is total electric w/back-up propane heat. Property is fenced & cross-fenced with corrals and ready for cattle! Improved Bermuda Grass & well water in each pasture. 30 x 50 shop w/electric & 20 x 50 equipment shed on the back, plus a 12 x 14 storage building. Nice storm cellar. Home has a lovely view and sits back off the highway on a hill. Additional land possibly available with the purchase of this home. Also, home may possibly be purchased with smaller acreage. Property has a fantastic water well & is situated over the Gerty Sands Aquifer. Please call Cindy at (580) 272-7820 for more information.
